ation: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000=
000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">In the JOBS Act</=
a>, Congress raised the threshold to 2,000 holders and excluded employee-co=
mpensation shares from the count. So now it is pretty improbable that a com=
pany would be forced to go public because it has gotten too big.</p><p styl=
